      "text": "Variable libraries\nwith environment-\nspecific value sets\nallows for dynamic\nconfiguration in\ndata pipelines,\nnotebooks,\ndataflow gen2,\netc. (no hard-\ncoded values)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Variable libraries with environment-specific value sets allows for dynamic configuration in data pipelines, notebooks, dataflow gen2, etc. (no hard-coded values)",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
